(1037, 1, '2021-03-12 12:15:44', '2021-03-12 12:15:44', 'Quick, intelligent, and playful. Fulfill the dream of a child and give him a private place to hang out. Teepee, will give your baby a sense of security and tranquility. Such an Indian wigwam is suitable even for the smallest.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Details:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Made of 100% midweight hypoallergenic cotton fabric</li>\r\n 	<li>Friendly, chemicals free fabrics - STANDARD 100 by OEKO-TEX</li>\r\n 	<li>Two large windows, one on each side</li>\r\n 	<li>Comes with 4 wooden poles</li>\r\n 	<li>Handcrafted with love in our family shop in Europe</li>\r\n 	<li>Options to add a mat, pillows, pouf, toy basket, flags</li>\r\n 	<li>Option to add a personalized teepee flag</li>\r\n 	<li>Adult assembly required</li>\r\n 	<li>1 Year Warranty</li>\r\n 	<li>Risk-Free, 30 Day Money Back Guarantee</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Dimensions small</strong>\r\n\r\nApprox size:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Width: 40\" 100cm</li>\r\n 	<li>Depth: 40\" 100cm</li>\r\n 	<li>Height: 48\" 120cm</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Dimensions large</strong>\r\n\r\nApprox size:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Width: 48\" 120cm</li>\r\n 	<li>Depth: 48\" 120cm</li>\r\n 	<li>Height: 63\" 160cm</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Installation</strong>\r\n\r\nFolds and sets up easily. No need to waste the whole afternoon trying to assemble it... Super easy, tool-free (and mom-friendly) installation.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Care</strong>\r\n\r\nMachine wash cold, use mild detergent, air dry only, do not bleach and iron inside out.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Shipping</strong>\r\n\r\nSince all teepees are made-to-order, it takes a few days to cut, sew, inspect, and pack your order. Teepees are usually shipped in 2-7 business days. If you do need your order sooner, reach out to us via phone, email or chat and we will do our best to accommodate. In most cases rush requests are shipped the next day.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Return &amp; Exchang